I've seen people arguing to #AbolishThePolice, and I've worried about what it even meant: wouldn't that be a disaster? But this thread of images summarizing info from https://t.co/6DeRjNKb5c gives a better sense of what (some) people mean by it: the general idea sounds promising! https://t.co/85NTkzH0gJ

Today, I read a great, long thread explaining what is meant by #AbolishThePolice, and I largely agreed by the end. 

But may I suggest: if you need a few hundred words on Twitter to explain a 3-word slogan, maybe you need a different slogan.
